Class SqlParserPos

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.sql.parser.SqlParserPos
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class SqlParserPos
extends Object
implements Serializable
    SqlParserPos represents the position of a parsed token within SQL statement text.
